            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic requiescit in pace Duion&amp;lt;a<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>&amp;gt; ancilla Ba<lb break="no" n="2"/>lentes <note>sic</note> e&amp;lt;t&amp;gt; sponsa Dextri deposita est III <lb n="3"/>Idus Sept<expan><ex>em</ex><abbr>b</abbr><ex>res</ex></expan> <surplus>consulatu</surplus> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> Theodosio <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> XIII et Valentiniano A<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>g</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> bes <note>sic</note> cc<expan><ex>on</ex><abbr>ss</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> adiu<lb break="no" n="5"/>ro per Deum et per leges C<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>resteanor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/>ut quicumque extraneus voluerit al<lb break="no" n="7"/>terum corpus ponere <surplus>voluerit</surplus> det <lb n="8"/>ec<expan><ex>c</ex><abbr>lisi</abbr><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> cat<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>olic</abbr><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>Sal</abbr><ex>onitanae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>aur</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> |(libras<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> III
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in situ mit der Bestattung darunter. Datierung: 426 n. Chr. (Theodosius cos. XII und Valentinian cos. II) oder 430 n. Chr. (Theodosius cos. XIII und Valentinian cos. III). Z. 8: zwischen AVR und III waagrechte Haste mit nach unten zeigenden cornua; nach J.-P. Caillet, in: Marin u. a., Salona 4 mit (pondo) oder (libras) aufzulösen.</p>
            </div>
